node.text: We stayed at @birunkumbet chalets yesterday. In the village at an altitude of 1700 meters, the chalets surrounded by pine trees make you feel really beautiful. The property also has a pool and sauna. This is a great option to escape the heat of summer. For more information, you can check out @birunkumbet account.
